{"id":24329,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/24329","type":2,"name":"砂ぼうず","name_cn":"砂和尚","summary":"　　关东大沙漠是一片可怕的死亡之地，数百年前，繁荣的文明毁于一旦，只留下沙海中默默矗立的高楼废墟，如墓碑般渲染着浓重的死亡气息。这里白天温度超过50摄氏度，到了夜晚又骤降到零下，环境极其恶劣。即使在这种地狱般的世界里，仍然活动着顽强的人类。\r\n　　关东沙漠通用的法则是金钱和力量，每个人都为自己的生存而战，各种丑恶的现象显得如此正常。其中有一个被称作“砂和尚”的少年，他原名水野灌太，对沙漠了如指掌的他在这里乾着代理人的工作，为了生存以及完成任务不择手段，因此被称作“沙漠的妖怪”。和他在一起的助手则是被称作“小沙”的女孩小泉太湖。在充满危险的大沙漠里，一个残酷的生存故事即将开始…… ","eps":[{"id":124973,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124973","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124974,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124974","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":1,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124975,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124975","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124976,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124976","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124977,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124977","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124978,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124978","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124979,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124979","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124980,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124980","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124981,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124981","type":0,"sort":9,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124982,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124982","type":0,"sort":10,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":124983,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/124983","type":0,"sort":11,"name":"","name_cn":"",